Package: miraculix
Version: 0.8.9
Title: Algebraic and Statistical Functions for Genetics
Author: Malena Erbe [aut, cre], Martin Schlather [aut, cre], Florian Skene [aut], Alexander Freudenberg [ctr]
Description: This is a collection fast tools (SIMD and OMP) needed in genetics, for instance, the calculation of the genetic relationship matrix. In particular, it is used in the breeding planning programme MoBPS at <https://github.com/tpook92/MoBPS>. It also contains the scanning approach by Kabluchko and Spodarev (2009), <doi:10.1239/aap/1240319575>.
Maintainer: Martin Schlather <afreuden@mail.uni-mannheim.de>
LinkingTo: RandomFieldsUtils
Depends: R (>= 3.0), RandomFieldsUtils (>= 0.5.3)
Imports: methods, graphics
Suggests:
License: GPL ( >= 3)
Biarch: true
URL: http://ms.math.uni-mannheim.de/de/publications/software/miraculix
NeedsCompilation: yes
